"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?23/15/23794?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Antithyroid drugs (Beyond the Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
